item.title: What do i type in for portforward
item.dc:creator: @ollie123 Ollie123
item.description:
@ollie123 wrote:

Application Name: PrivateServer
Port Range: 43594-43594 (Repace with your actual server port, could be 5555)
Protocol: Both
IP Address: Whatever your local IP address is
Enable: Yes
